\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Calliope makes available flat, sharp, cancellation, and mixed key signatures in a variety of styles.  Individual pitch signs may be doubled at the octave in accordance with 17th century practice.  Signs may appear in modern or old book style or in chant notation.   Any change in a key signature's attributes may optionally cause the appropriate transposition of the music controlled by the key signature.  The placement of a key signature is handled automatically according to the nearest clef that governs it.  Non-conventional features include mixed signatures of flats and sharps, and the ability to move signatures to different pitch centres.\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 \par
